@Node Requirements "Fortis: System requirements"

@{u}@{fg shine}Requirements:@{fg text}@{uu}

- operating system: MorphOS 3.14
  (http://www.morphos.net),

- hardware: PowerPC computers supported by MorphOS 3.14
  (at this moment: Pegasos 1/2 G3/G4, Efika, MacMini G3/G4, eMac, iBook G3
  PowerBook G3/G4, PowerMac G3/G4),

- graphics card: Voodoo 4/5, ATI Radeon (supported
  by 3D drivers in MorphOS 3.14),

- memory: at least 45MB of free RAM,

- hard disk: at least 40MB of free disk space,

- PowerSDL version 16.1 or higher
  (http://aminet.net/util/libs/powersdl.lha).


The latest version of the Fortis game hasn't been tested on MorphOS in version 
lower than 3.14. However is possible that the game works on earlier versions
of the MorphOS.


