@Node Installation "Fortis: Installation"

@{u}@{fg shine}Installation@{fg text}@{uu}

The Fortis has no hard disk installer. Just unarchive the Fortis LHA archive
into a location on your hard disk where you would like Fortis to be.
The application will be ready for use.

Be sure that PowerSDL 16.1 or higher has been already installed in your system.

If you use computer with graphics card with 32MB video RAM (MacMini, eMac),
please disable 3D Layers in MorphOS. You can also try run the game on low
resolution screen (for example 800x600).


@{u}@{fg shine}Uninstallation@{fg text}@{uu}

For uninstalling just delete the drawer containing the Fortis.


